{"word":"G5158 - τρόπος - trópos - trop'-os - As","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τρόπος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>trópos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>trop'-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>As"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"சேர்த்துக் கொள்ளும் வண்ணம், அப்படியே, பிரகாரம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. a manner, way, fashion"},{"paragraph":"2. manner of life, character"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; a <i>turn</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>mode</i> or <i>style</i> (especially with preposition or relatively prefixed as adverb <i>like</i>); figuratively <i>deportment</i> or <i>character:</i> - (even) as, conversation, [+ like] manner (+ by any) means, way."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5158 - τρόπος - trópos - trop'-os/5158\">G5158</a>, <a href=\"#/G5159 - τροποφορέω - tropophoréō - trop-of-or-eh'-o/5159\">G5159</a>"}]}